s=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 23, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xfc1665703196971.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xfc1665703196971.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xfc1665703196971.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xfc1665703196971\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Reload the Uniface Router’s assignment file.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xfc1665703196971__section_bpn_jrr_gwb\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xfc1665703196971__p_d135356e1_d135357e1_d135358e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">operation UROUTER_ASNRELOAD</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xfc1665703196971__section_ow2_mrr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d751470e57\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xfc1665703196971__section_btl_nrr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d751470e66\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to 0. Otherwise, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html#qln1665702528769__section_fbt_4d2_gwb\">Return Codes</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xfc1665703196971__section_bqv_rrr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d751470e82\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xfc1665703196971__section_rdq_srr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d751470e91\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The privileged-user operation <span class=\"keyword apiname\">UROUTER_ASNRELOAD</span> causes the Uniface\n        Router to reread its assignment file. All settings are set to those specified in the\n        assignment file. All dynamically altered values in the Uniface Router and the USTs are\n        reset.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Although all values are reset, only those values that pertain to starting and stopping\n        servers have an effect. Changing the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DEFAULT_NET</span> setting has no effect,\n        because the Uniface Router that uses that setting is not re-executed.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533690\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533690\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UROUTER_ASNRELOAD Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 23, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Reload the Uniface Router’s assignment file. operation UROUTER_ASNRELOAD Parameters None. Return Values If successful, $status is set to 0. Otherwise, see Return Codes . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The privileged-user operation UROUTER_ASNRELOAD causes the Uniface Router to reread its assignment file. All settings are set to those specified in the assignment file. All dynamically altered values in the Uniface Router and the USTs are reset. Although all values are reset, only those values that pertain to starting and stopping servers have an effect. Changing the $DEFAULT_NET setting has no effect, because the Uniface Router that uses that setting is not re-executed. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}